@thethingy

I'm interested in knowing if these typefaces can be considered licensed? Do you think it's possible for someone looking at these fonts to tell they were not purchased? As a graphic design student I hear lots of distaste among the field towards the use of unlicensed fonts. Yet I support piracy and I'm conflicted due to my chosen line of work's negative view on it.

Anyways, just wondered. Very grateful for your torrents, they've helped me save quite a bit of money. Just wondering if I can proudly and openly use these without being harassed/sued-by-clients/etc. :D
